---
title: Mediterranean Style Chicken and Avocado Sunshine Salad with Roasted Pepper, Greek Style Cheese and Pesto Drizzle
description: A bowl of summer sun, this Mediterranean Style Chicken Breast and Avocado Sunshine Salad is perfect for a balanced lifestyle. Inspired by Greek and Italian cuisines whilst heroing fresh veg, this is sure to hit the spot.
